title: Birdsong
lyrics:
Birdsong
Cutting up the night
Swimming through the atmosphere
Got stuck
Reaching for a place
Thousand miles away from here



Ocean pass, a shiver in the westward

Stop strobing this way

'Cause the tide is standing over us

I watch it fade away
